txt.en: The vile Ongûl has taken Thoremband, the Guarded Court. If the White Company is to gain control over the city, this minion of Minas Morgul must be removed.
Ongûl can be found at Thoremband upon the Circle of Death.\n\nYou should defeat Ongûl.
The vile Ongûl has taken Thoremband and must be removed.
Ongûl can be found at Thoremband upon the Circle of Death.\n\nYou should defeat Ongûl.
You have defeated the vile Ongûl and provided a great service to the White Company. Their efforts to reclaim Minas Ithil are now ever closer thanks to you.
